---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Primorum"
  description="Expert AI workflows that complete defined business outcomes, priced on success."
>
  <p class="eyebrow">Primorum</p>

  <h1 class="hero">
    Expert AI workflows, priced on outcomes.
  </h1>

  <p class="lede">
    Most AI agents charge by usage, whether or not the work gets done. Primorum operates
    expert AI workflows that complete defined business outcomes, and bills only when the
    outcome is delivered.
  </p>

  <p>
    Each workflow is built around a specific, bounded result &mdash; a market dossier, a
    qualified pipeline, a filed application. Primorum builds the workflow, runs it, reviews
    the work, and stands behind it. If the agreed result is not produced, the engagement
    is refunded.
  </p>

  <hr class="divider" />

  <h2>Workflows</h2>

  <p class="lede" style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
    Engagements start at $9,000, priced per outcome.
  </p>

  <ul class="bets">
    <li>
      <p class="label">Market intelligence</p>
      <p class="claim">
        A board-ready briefing on a target segment, with named players, sized
        opportunity, and a defensible go/no-go recommendation.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p class="label">Sales pipeline</p>
      <p class="claim">
        A qualified pipeline of meetings booked with named accounts that match a defined
        ideal customer profile.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p class="label">Talent search</p>
      <p class="claim">
        A shortlist of vetted candidates for a defined role, with screening notes and
        outreach completed.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p class="label">Filings &amp; applications</p>
      <p class="claim">
        Trademark, regulatory, or administrative filings completed end-to-end &mdash;
        researched, drafted, submitted, and tracked.
      </p>
    </li>
  </ul>

  <hr class="divider" />

  <h2>How engagements work</h2>

  <ul class="rules">
    <li>
      <p class="num">01</p>
      <p class="rule">A bounded outcome.</p>
      <p>
        Each engagement is defined by a single, written result. If the result is
        ambiguous, Primorum will not take the engagement.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p class="num">02</p>
      <p class="rule">An expert workflow, not a chat session.</p>
      <p>
        Each workflow is a dedicated AI system designed for a category of work, reviewed
        before delivery.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p class="num">03</p>
      <p class="rule">Priced per result.</p>
      <p>
        Engagements start at $9,000 and are priced against the outcome, not against time
        spent or tokens consumed.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p class="num">04</p>
      <p class="rule">Refunded if not delivered.</p>
      <p>
        If the agreed result is not produced, the engagement is refunded in full. The
        standard for delivery is written into the engagement before work begins.
      </p>
    </li>
  </ul>

  <hr class="divider" />

  <h2>Begin an engagement</h2>

  <p>
    Engagements are intake-only. Describe the outcome you need; Primorum will respond
    with a scoping document, a fixed price, and the standard for delivery before work
    begins.
  </p>

  <p style="margin-top: 2rem;">
    <a href="mailto:engage@primorum.ai">engage@primorum.ai</a>
  </p>
</Base>
